casebody.data:
Paul MEYER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4431 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

As the petitioner at the commissioner's hearing on April 17, 2018, voluntarily withdrew the petition for belated appeal, the petition is dismissed.

LaROSE, C.J., and KELLY and LUCAS, JJ., Concur.
